<L>Be fore the king on kne &s;ett,</L>
<L>And on hir langage &s;cho him grett.</L>
<L>"Lauerid<NOTE N="s" PLACE="foot">Lord.</NOTE> king, Wa&s;&s;aille," &s;eid &s;che.</L>
