<L>Sperde<NOTE N="x" PLACE="foot">Clo&s;ed, &s;hut. In P. Plowman, of a blind man. <Q REND="inline"><HI>"un&s;parryd</HI> his eine."</Q> i. e. opened his eyes.</NOTE> with manie a dyvers pynne.</L>
