<P>His FIFTEEN TOKNES<NOTE N="k" PLACE="foot">Tokens.</NOTE> BEFORE THE DAY OF JUDGMENT, are taken from the prophet Jeremiah.</P>
<Q><L>The fir&s;t &s;igne thar ageins, as our lord hym&s;elfe &s;ede,</L>
