<P>We have then this de&s;cription of the New Jeru&s;alem.</P>
<Q><L>This citie is y&s;et on an hei hille,</L>
<L>That no &s;ynful man may therto tille <NOTE N="s" PLACE="foot">Come.</NOTE>:</L>
