<L>And &s;o fayr berel may non be y&s;ene.</L>
<L>Thulke hyl is nougt elles to under&s;tondynge</L>
<L>Bote holi thugt, and de&s;yr brennynge,</L>
<L>The whuche holi men hadde heer to that place,</L>
<L>Whiles hi hadde on eorthe here lyves &s;pace;</L>
<L>And i likne, as ymay ymagene in my thougt,</L>
<L>The walles of hevene, to walles that were ywrougt</L>
<L>Of all maner preciou&s;e &s;tones y&s;et yfere <NOTE N="t" PLACE="foot">Together.</NOTE>,</L>
<L>And y&s;emented with gold brigt and clere;</L>
<L>Bot &s;o brigt gold, ne non &s;o clene,</L>
